    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，双写指的是同时写入IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream（旧系统）和新的IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic。10月20日进入第三阶段，回填历史数据，确保新系统有完整的数据基线。然后10月25日做流量切换，把读流量切到新路径上。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "2025-10-20",
        "2025-10-25",
        "Backfill historical data",
        "Flip reads to new path (IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic)",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经把前四个节点画出来了：10/1设计新形态、10/10双写、10/20回填、10/25读流量切换。最后一个节点是11月5日移除旧写入，我理解就是停止往IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream写数据，只保留新系统的写入路径。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "2025-11-05",
        "Remove old writes (IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，10月25日那个节点我需要调整一下描述。之前我说\"读流量切到新路径\"，但更准确的说法是\"Flip reads to new path (IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic)\"——需要明确标注切换的目标系统。另外确认一下，整个时间线的标题格式没问题吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "2025-10-25",
        "Flip reads to new path (IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic)"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "已修正，10月25日的节点现在明确标注了IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic。标题\"Schema Evolution (IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode)\"格式正确。我再核对一遍五个节点：10/1 Design new shape + feature flags，10/10 Dual-write old+new，10/20 Backfill historical data，10/25 Flip reads to new path (IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic)，11/5 Remove old writes (IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream)。顺序和依赖关系都符合渐进式迁移的安全原则。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Schema Evolution (IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode)",
        "2025-10-01",
        "2025-10-10",
        "2025-10-20",
        "2025-10-25",
        "2025-11-05"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "完美。补充一个细节：双写阶段我们加了feature flags做保护，万一新系统有问题可以秒级回切。这个在10月1日的节点里用\"+ feature flags\"体现了。整个演进的核心就是先并行、再迁移、后下线，确保IoT工业边缘节点的数据连续性。",
